Package: conditionalFD
Title: Identification of Conditional Front Doors and Adjustment Sets
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Felix", "Thoemmes", , "fjt36@cornell.edu", role = c("aut")),
    person("Arin", "Barde", , "asb385@cornell.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Jiwoo", "Kim", , "jk2759@cornell.edu", role = c("aut")))
Description: Implements methods based on Pearl (2009) for identifying front-door mediator sets in directed acyclic graphs (DAGs). The package builds on functionality from the 'dagitty' package and uses d-separation criteria to enumerate and validate valid front-door sets.
